1
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:36,519
Stop right there!

2
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:38,120
After him! Hurry!

3
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:38,959
Get him!

4
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,920
After him! Stop right there!

5
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,959
Freeze!

6
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,920
Hurry!

7
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,640
Faster!

8
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:51,120
Don't let him get away!

9
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,280
Get him!

10
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:53,920
Stop!

11
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:57,599
Hurry up! After him!

12
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:59,040
Stop right there!

13
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,639
Get him!

14
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,439
After him!

15
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:32,280
Quick, after him!

16
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,560
Go, get him!

17
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:35,919
Move it!

18
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:36,919
Keep after him!

19
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,520
After him! Don't lose him!

20
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,919
Stop!

21
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,280
Stop right there!

22
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,039
Faster!

23
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:43,879
Hurry up!

24
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,159
Move faster!

25
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:49,639
After him!

26
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,319
Go!

27
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:52,919
Hurry!

28
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,919
Keep up!

29
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,800
After him!

30
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:49,719
Go, hurry!

31
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,719
Hurry, go get help!

32
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:01,400
You stop me from unleashing my ultimate.

33
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,759
Go!

34
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:03,439
Get help!

35
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:03,960
Okay.

36
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,599
I don't even have an ultimate!

37
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,560
Sorry,

38
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,000
but I never hit girls.

39
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:58,839
Looks like you really are afraid of me.

40
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,720
But no one can ever bring me down.

41
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:33,120
Don't fear your body's limitations.

42
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,879
Calm your mind and look within,

43
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:37,720
and you'll possess limitless power.

44
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,519
Yang Yunfan has changed.

45
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,879
We're no match for him.

46
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,519
Let's fall back for now.

47
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,800
You sure can run, huh?

48
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,519
Take him down!

49
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:23,600
Boss.

50
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,879
He looks a bit off, you know.

51
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,759
Take him down!

52
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,639
Get him!

53
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,799
Someone's head fell off!

54
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,360
Why am I buried alive again?

55
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:28,799
Did I botch this character build?

56
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,759
Did it force me to restart?

57
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,240
That can't be right.

58
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:36,360
The Earth energy is insufficient.

59
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,960
The yin meridian isn't unblocked.

60
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:42,159
Yellow earth secures three parts of life.

61
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:45,720
Grass roots sustain energy for the soul.

62
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,320
Please, I'm begging you, don't kill me!

63
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:48,919
I heal the sick and save lives.

64
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:49,440
I don't smoke or drink.

65
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:49,919
I'm strong and healthy.

66
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:50,360
Quite the smooth talker too.

67
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,320
And not bad-looking, either.

68
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,360
If you promise not to kill me,

69
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,639
I swear I'll visit you this time every year.

70
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,639
So noisy.

71
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:58,039
I shouldn't have bothered scaring you.

72
00:09:58,039 --> 00:10:00,000
Didn't realize you valued your life so much.

73
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,080
Ye Qingxue!

74
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,919
Why is a Miss CEO awake so late at night,

75
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:04,399
playing dress-up as the White Reaper?

76
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,720
Your injuries are too severe.

77
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,080
If I don't bury you, how can I save you?

78
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,039
Couldn't you just put me on an IV drip?

79
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,960
Or take me to the apothecary?

80
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,679
Did you really have to bury me?

81
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:15,120
We can't go to the apothecary.

82
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,519
I'm not sure if it's safe there.

83
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:20,000
This is the Ye family's ancestral secret art.

84
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,159
Use medicine to replenish Earth energy,

85
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,840
nurture the meridians,

86
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,639
grass roots channel energy to revive you.

87
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:28,919
This is the Life-Restoring Art of the Medicine King.

88
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:29,720
Works every single time.

89
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,759
This is hardly channeling energy.

90
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:34,200
This is straight-up summoning spirits!

91
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,720
And what's with all these heads?

92
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,559
Playing Candy Crush?

93
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,399
I'm still alive, you know!

94
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:41,799
You'll get used to it after a few times.

95
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:43,600
There's no need to visit a place like this twice!

96
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,799
What are you doing?

97
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:52,600
This is my head,

98
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,519
not a watermelon!

99
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:55,120
Just checking if it's ripe yet.

100
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,840
So what am I, then?

101
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,679
A freshly unearthed fiancé?

102
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,399
Right now,

103
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:06,240
according to the Ye Family's Mental Method,

104
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,000
you're only half a Medicinal subject.

105
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,200
Not fully ripe yet.

106
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,120
Your Ye family's methods are too wild.

107
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:13,759
I'm about to turn into a Beggar's Chicken!

108
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,120
Let's try my method instead.

109
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,720
Hey!

110
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,200
Why are you taking off your clothes?

111
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,159
What kind of method is this?

112
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:29,240
If I don't take off my clothes,

113
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,279
how will I absorb the medicinal vapor?

114
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:38,960
Absorb medicinal vapor?

115
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,240
Then I'll go fetch you a pharmacist.

116
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:48,720
Ye Qingxue!

117
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,000
You're too cold-hearted!

118
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:53,919
Who did I get injured for?

119
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:55,960
Now you're just going to leave me here?

120
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,559
Just go.

121
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,440
And don't come back!

122
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,200
I...

123
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,120
The esteemed Young Lady of the Ye family

124
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,200
doesn't even know basic pharmacology?

125
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,120
I do know.

126
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,200
I remember all the acupoints.

127
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:26,759
It's just...

128
00:12:26,759 --> 00:12:28,519
I've never done it hands-on before.

129
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,759
I'm afraid I'll mess it up.

130
00:12:39,919 --> 00:12:41,000
Since your medical skills are so good,

131
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:42,720
why don't you do it yourself?

132
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,279
What's wrong?

133
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,039
I think

134
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,320
my energy hasn't stabilized yet,

135
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,399
and I can't clearly see my own acupoints.

136
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,240
I'm feeling a bit weak.

137
00:13:06,639 --> 00:13:07,720
It's okay.

138
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,519
I can do it.

139
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,399
Let me help you.

140
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,399
Where's the second acupoint?

141
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:23,720
Right here.

142
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:37,519
Here?

143
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,120
Okay.

144
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,879
What's wrong?

145
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:01,480
Does it hurt a lot?

146
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:02,919
No.

147
00:14:03,639 --> 00:14:05,159
It's just a bit itchy.

148
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,519
Are you blushing?

149
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,519
It's not like you haven't seen it before.

150
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:16,919
I...

151
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,120
I...

152
00:14:19,879 --> 00:14:21,960
I'm just afraid of getting it wrong

153
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,639
and hindering your recovery.

154
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,279
Then hurry and find the third acupoint.

155
00:14:33,759 --> 00:14:35,960
Third is the Shenque acupoint (the navel).

156
00:14:47,279 --> 00:14:48,240
Right on the navel.

157
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:52,879
What are you looking at me for?

158
00:14:52,879 --> 00:14:53,799
I'm looking at the acupoint!

159
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:57,480
Here.

160
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,080
Yes.

161
00:14:59,519 --> 00:15:00,360
Okay.

162
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,639
Feeling better?

163
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:23,639
Miss Ye.

164
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:24,799
I know you work out,

165
00:15:25,279 --> 00:15:27,320
but if you tense your muscles like this,

166
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,360
I really can't stick them on.

167
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,159
Miss Ye, my bad...

168
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,399
I...

169
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:52,200
I'm done.

170
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:52,679
Okay.

171
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:53,519
I'll be going now.

172
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,159
Um...

173
00:15:55,159 --> 00:15:55,759
Wait a sec.

174
00:15:55,759 --> 00:15:56,120
Who

175
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:56,799
is gonna help me take these off later?

176
00:16:41,279 --> 00:16:43,080
What's the rush?

177
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,879
It's not going to be over that quickly.
